Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.63,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:08.36,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,There have been some bad rumors about Her Highness, Princess Euphemia but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.24,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,You're referring to the incident at Kaminejima, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.11,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,It has been said that she came into contact with Zero during it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.03,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's connected to the top level?{go back to}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.39,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:19.03,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,The Governor-General isn't the only one questioning her actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.71,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, if they are connected to that side...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.75,CG ON,???01,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we need to break off any ties with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:25.25,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:29.32,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,We have gathered all the evidence, Undersecretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.65,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,You have been receiving benefits from the NAC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:33.90,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,General Darlton, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.49,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:41.20,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I can finally eliminate those insolent fools who exploited His Highness Clovis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:46.25,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Her Highness Princess Euphemia's idea for a Specially Administrated Zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:50.15,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,the number of rats that were thrown into confusion was a lot larger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:00:57.95,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,The number of applicants for the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon has exceeded 200,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.20,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this figure will continue to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.75,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:02.50,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.50,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because someone like you, a representative of the Japanese people, is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:08.42,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone believes in this place, right? {Dakara koso}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:12.95,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's because it was an announcement from a Princess herself, isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:15.55,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I really am... thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:17.50,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I should be the one thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:21.10,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You will help me with various things in the future, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.28,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:23.25,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.10,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:07.12,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time that Britannia has tried to make something like the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:10.76,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,and it is something Princess Euphemia herself decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.22,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,Considering that Her Highness was still a student just a few days back before she announced this radical plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.05,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,we can't deny the possibility of that fact influencing her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.84,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's something Princess Euphemia said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.84,CG ON,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.56,CG ON,Annoucement,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, the plan is being carried out smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:24.18,CG ON,Annoucement,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's ceremony will be broadcasted to the whole world. {Asu no shikiten...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.44,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:30.99,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the terrorist cells within Area 11 will lose the support of the people and collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.27,CG ON,Schneiser,0000,0000,0000,,Public order will be restored too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.46,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'm against this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:39.13,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,But you understand. That's why you sent Darlton to assist her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.76,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I must put an officially announced political measure into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.82,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,That is the obvious step for me to take as the Governor-General.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.02,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.16,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to accept what is going to happen to Euphie from an official standpoint?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.33,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon. That isn't something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:58.05,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Can we find any value in the Japan they give us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.94,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,The current situation is the result of our resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.22,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to feel ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:08.18,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kirihara, I heard that, due to your close ties with the extraction of Sakuradite,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:11.47,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,you have been promised a considerable position within the Specially Administrated Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:15.18,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing. I am just invited to attend the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.97,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What a good excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:17.90,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,You all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.01,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,What about Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.82,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,What will the Order of the Black Knights do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.25,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:30.24,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Not only our supporters, but also members of the Order are showing interest in joining the Specially Administrated Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.67,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,The Specially Administrated Zone is different from the Order of the Black Knights since there aren't any risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:39.60,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's a princess from an established lineage compared to a masked man whose identity is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.01,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Just based on looks alone, it's obvious which side is more dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.71,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto said that they are going to support them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:45.96,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.85,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Because they said that we'll be treated equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.77,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Equally? Words alone can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.31,CG ON,Shogo,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:55.69,CG ON,Shogo,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't decide upon a countermeasure soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.52,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,You say that you want to join the Specially Administrated Zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:03.46,CG ON,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, it doesn't matter if you're a Britannian or an Eleven...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.40,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:09.20,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we follow Euphemia's proposal and have the Order of the Black Knights join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.62,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,As I was saying, a promise from Britannia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.96,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,What Zero said doesn't contradict with joining the Specially Administrated Zone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.39,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.79,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,They will use the pretense of peace to force us to disarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.57,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,That will be troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:26.02,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,We will be controlled by the system and lose our independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:29.72,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,However, we will be branded as the enemy of freedom and equality if we don't join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.24,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we should join them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.02,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's no guarantee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.10,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't ignore this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.29,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you take a side trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.63,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you accompanied me to buy stuff after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.98,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're going to meet up with Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.49,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she wants to buy something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.62,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Lately there have been too many disturbances due to the creation of the Specially Administrated Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:50.90,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.92,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, isn't it better for you to hurry and patch things up with Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.41,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about the Specially Administrated Zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.14,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about providing support?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.96,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Who would sign for such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.40,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.67,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.97,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't equality already in place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:07.21,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Those below should be obedient and listen to those on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:11.73,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, that is the true reason behind the benevolence of the Vice Governor-General.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.24,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:17.55,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You feel great looking down at people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.65,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Student, that's enough. Step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.56,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:31.31,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(690,0)}Yes, I should. I shall take my leave here then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.76,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.58,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.85,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mr. Aristocrat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:41.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't confuse borrowed strength with your own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:44.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A bastard like you should just die without people knowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.84,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, let's stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.02,CG ON,Rivalz,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy, why don't you say something apologetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.84,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,I-Insolent! I am...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.50,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.56,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:01.41,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He saved an Eleven, even though he is Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.23,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, because he IS Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.90,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's so, why was he together with Princess Euphemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:10.07,CG ON,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it might become dangerous if I delve too deeply into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:17.84,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,NAC. No, it seems that you're called "Kyoto" among the terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.96,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,You will dissolve during the ceremony tomorrow and leave Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:25.34,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,We are willing to discuss carrying on our business dealings with you if you dissolve unconditionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.76,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,, Of course you must cease your support of the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:35.89,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Whether Zero comes tomorrow or not, that man's defeat has already been ascertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:39.89,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.07,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.15,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shirley-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in the end she didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.02,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't contact her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.05,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's teaching you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.20,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you have been acting coldly towards her lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.38,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reflect upon my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:56.28,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sayoko-san, can you get me a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.54,CG ON,Sayoko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.71,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something that you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.52,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.48,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,About Sister Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.42,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say something willful like "I want to see her again."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.84,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Since it will cause trouble for Brother, as well as Sister Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.15,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Euphie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:21.11,CG ON,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Brother, you like her as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.94,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I did like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.32,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,This is the site where the memorial ceremony for the establishment of the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon is being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:35.30,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,The site is filled with Elevens, no, Japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:39.67,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,A large number of Japanese people who couldn't get in have gathered outside of the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:43.18,CG ON,Annoucement02,0000,0000,0000,,Lesley-san, has Zero appeared yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.15,CG ON,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,No, it seems that, even now, he hasn't contacted anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:50.92,CG ON,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(571,557)\an8\fs22\i1}Note: Yao Long Zhi Fang literally means "House of Biting Dragons" in Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:51.34,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't Zero come? He wouldn't appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:55.26,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The data we have on him should be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.32,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.17,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.20,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.20,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.62,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Zero appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.20,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You've arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.54,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Did you accept your defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.83,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.51,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I intended to bring your identity with me to my grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.99,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything will come to an end if the fact that Zero is a prince of Britannia is revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:40.51,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will be mistakenly thought that this is all a plot going on between Britannians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.68,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be the end of this Specially Administrated Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.07,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,The target is Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.76,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him if anything abnormal happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.35,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.81,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.65,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.96,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia Li Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to discuss with you after I land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.01,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.62,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.43,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Something major has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.04,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Zero has appeared in a majestic manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.71,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,He's now heading towards the G1 base according to Princess Euphemia's instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.80,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we should have gone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.56,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:19.18,CG ON,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,"Zero won't appear if Lancelot is standing there ready and waiting." Everyone was saying that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.60,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.07,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.33,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.20,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed too dangerous to be left alone with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.73,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.90,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. Please believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:40.24,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long are we going to stay here and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.24,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero told us to wait here. Don't you trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.66,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.92,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was done to confirm Britannia's real intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:48.83,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.75,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:54.54,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we know their intentions that our entire force is lying in ambush in every direction, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.84,CG ON,Ohgi,0000,0000,0000,,Assumption is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:59.01,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Even Diethard and Rakshata are on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.43,CG ON,Tohdoh,0000,0000,0000,,Zero is most likely intending to make Euphemia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.95,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.05,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,The camera has already been switched off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It because I've always been hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.87,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to a certain Imperial Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.45,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is a ceramic needlegun. {Needlegun is one word}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Detectors can't find this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.82,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, you won't fire at me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.48,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I won't fire at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.63,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, the one firing it will be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:25.74,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.71,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's all right. She's alone with Zero after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.45,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:33.17,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,I've handed her a call switch to notify us during an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:50.85,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.04,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you with Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.46,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:59.19,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Is it due to the influence of the close contact and the incident at Kaminejima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.77,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Or is this guy also...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.11,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.97,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This ceremony is being broadcasted around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:16.46,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,During it, if a princess of Britannia, like you, fires a shot at Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.80,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.96,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,A revolt will break out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Zero will become a martyr if he was tricked into being shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.55,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Your popularity will drop to rock bottom as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.90,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.62,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Together with me, we'll make Nippon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just unilaterally forcing your opinions down upon others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.14,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the same as what Clovis did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:34.73,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All the conditions have already been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:41.99,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Zero will hover between life and death before reviving miraculously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.93,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,People react easier to miracles than reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.28,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.01,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There can only be one messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:55.21,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Once the people realize that you're a fake, the people will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.88,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I-Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.55,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,I only want to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.05,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.55,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.03,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.04,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Major Kururugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.42,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch, what did you just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.59,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.64,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.47,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop feeling pity for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:31.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept sympathy from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.71,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try and achieve it with my own power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.25,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to taint myself to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.92,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia Li Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.84,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I have already relinquished that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.60,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I think it won't be long before the main country announces it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.78,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I have relinquished my rights to succeed to the throne as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.43,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's because you accepted Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.41,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Since they listened to my selfish request,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.31,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,in return I have to pay an appropriate price, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:03.47,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You sure abandoned it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to say it was for my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:07.96,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you sure are conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.37,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Nunnally's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:16.03,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That girl said that she doesn't need anything else as long as she can stay with her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.06,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.00,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind just because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:25.76,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It made me think about what is most important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:31.80,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, that is why, I won't abandon anything that is really, really important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.43,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I didn't say anything about the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What about Cornelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.86,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if I won't get to see her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.11,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.45,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A big idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:49.28,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, even though I have never beaten you in a game or academically...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:55.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, because of your recklessness, you managed to attain everything in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:15:00.20,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, before you're a Vice Govenor-General or a princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,you're just Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.84,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm just Euphie, are you willing to work together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.06,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.28,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,you're the worst kind of enemy I face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.60,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.37,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.22,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Lets plan how we can make this Specially Administrated Zone survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.60,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but I don't intend to become your subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.67,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.74,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure don't have any confidence in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.53,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:32.11,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, you thought that I would shoot you if you threatened me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.91,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, you're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:37.63,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No one is able to go against any order I give, if I'm serious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:41.00,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,"Shoot me." "Relieve Suzaku from duty."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.52,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same no matter what order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.25,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you keep cracking weird jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.44,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.84,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if I say "Kill the Japanese."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.32,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.31,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,No... I... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.26,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.80,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.42,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:13.07,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I must kill the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.39,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:18.12,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(330,400)\i1}I've become like Mao. I can't turn off my Geass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.54,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the order I just gave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.65,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.48,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:28.42,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since I've finished my discussion with the Chinese Federation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.09,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back to the main country today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.40,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,But the experimental specimen is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.14,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, what about his mental abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.71,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to what we can do in Area 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:38.93,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.81,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to the laboratory in Rosenberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.94,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,Can you send him over together with the experimental machine as a set once I've contacted them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.18,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.62,CG ON,Bartley,0000,0000,0000,,Also, about the miracle that happened at Kaminejima...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.74,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait for public order to be restored in Area 11 first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.91,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful that the Specially Administrated Zone was created to accomplish that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:17:00.24,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Euphemia that everything has proceeded along smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.13,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Govenor-General, where's Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.42,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who calls themselves Japanese:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.93,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.81,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Can you all die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:08.35,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.48,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What did she just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.25,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,She's lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.31,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:12.67,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Suzaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.48,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he just lose consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.79,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.18,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.60,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that you would all commit suicide, but is that impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:25.71,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can all the soldiers please annihilate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.83,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's a massacre!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:28.36,CG ON,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is she serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.94,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Cut off the microphones and cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.36,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:31.92,CG ON,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.28,CG ON,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You terrorist...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:35.95,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Move away!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.52,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Now, will all the soldiers please hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.63,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Euphemia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.46,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.13,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop. Doing such things is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.72,CG ON,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:02.43,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... But I must annihilate the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.85,CG ON,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, everyone from Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.64,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Kill the Elevens. Eliminate all the Elevens with all your effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:13.76,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let even one escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:15.82,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:19.19,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an Honorary Knight from Britannia, Kururugi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.78,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the battle right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.33,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Our orders are to obliterate the Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.21,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It was issued by Princess Euphemia herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.25,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What? By Princess Euphemia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.62,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying something so foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.05,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,You're Japanese, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.37,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.36,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.33,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Gun salute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.00,CG ON,???04,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be possible. What about the television?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.11,CG ON,???05,0000,0000,0000,,The broadcast has been terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.11,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.68,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was... caused by my Geass...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.27,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:55.13,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Our... Japan's... Savior...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:01.07,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither a savior nor a messiah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.77,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,You're... our hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.41,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.75,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't... don't force it on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.58,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does this mean I have to bear this sin and try to atone for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.66,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.37,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.59,CG ON,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, what did you do to Princess Euphemia...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Andreas Darlton...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:27.27,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The most trusted among those trusted by Cornelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.67,CG ON,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is going on in the venue?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.10,CG ON,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confirming it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.77,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Erm... venue... confirm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.17,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we unable to turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.75,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that someone is hacking in from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.86,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. This is being broadcasted around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.24,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,They will terminate the broadcast soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.76,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Upload the data to the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.71,CG ON,Rakshata,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.34,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.06,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Staff officer, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.72,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that C.C. has met up with the Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:53.06,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. There shouldn't be any problems left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:57.34,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you crafted this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.01,CG ON,Diethard,0000,0000,0000,,but this battle is proceeding better than what we planned, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.48,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,It was shocking. You actually went so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.49,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:08.68,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,What? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:11.18,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use my Geass...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.73,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't intend to use my Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.23,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Indeed, what happened earlier was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:22.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I made the contract knowing it. I knew how dangerous this power could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.66,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:31.04,CG ON,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,That fellow finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.71,CG ON,Schneizel,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.67,CG ON,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Cornelia, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.92,CG ON,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if only those who can keep up with me follow me into combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.43,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.72,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found her? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.09,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.77,CG ON,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I can't contact General Darlton either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.44,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.69,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's too different from how Princess Euphemia usually acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:58.05,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right if they are still open for negotiations, but I'm unable to contact Kirihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.86,CG ON,???03,0000,0000,0000,,For now, even if it's just us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.33,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. What about the gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.17,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:03.78,CG ON,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:06.45,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you just value your own lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.21,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Sumeragi, please mind your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.91,CG ON,???02,0000,0000,0000,,We must carry on living for the sake of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.15,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do if we are the only ones left?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:15.53,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already, Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.88,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a girl that is dependant on the status of her family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.46,CG ON,Kaguya,0000,0000,0000,,What is Kyoto for if we don't act now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:23.46,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that Euphie would issue a massacre order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.30,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I must find her.... Find Euphie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:34.01,CG ON,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the Britannian army has come out of the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:38.58,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Since things have turned out like this, I have no choice but to make full use of Euphie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.69,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That... is the only thing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.47,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,To the terrorist: return that machine to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.20,CG ON,???,0000,0000,0000,,That belongs to our army...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:50.72,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Inform all the members of the Order of the Black Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.24,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Euphemia has become our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:57.83,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Specially Administrated Zone of Nippon is nothing but a despicable trap used to lure us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:02.13,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The various Mobile Humanoid Combat Armored Knight units will break into the ceremonial venue!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:06.62,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We will exterminate the Britannians and rescue the Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.55,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:12.47,CG ON,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie... she'll... she'll definitely...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.74,CG ON,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Be found and killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:50.23,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who caused it... this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:53.10,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Whose sin is it... this tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:56.29,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who desired it... this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:59.75,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who does it belong to... this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:01.69,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:04.67,CG Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But, even so, at least I'll...!
